To install this program:
-----------------------

1. Make sure you have GNU Scientific Library installed.
   Easiest is via homebrew:

   $ brew install gsl

2. Make and Make clean

   $ make && make clean

The make clean command will leave the binary file in a ./bin subdirectory.


To run, simply
-------------

  $ ./bin/MeanShiftGPU [seed]

where seed is an optional integer argument, specifying the random seed used to generate input data.

